Overview Notes: Vit D: supplement with vit D and recheck in 4/12, aim for 50-80 ng/ml. VitD is important for your bones;mood and cognitive health. Has anti-inflammatory, anti-cancer properties.

Overview Notes: Cholesterol: try to manage with lifestyle alone. Healthy diet, continue exercising, decrease your weekend alcohol consumption&manage stress. Supplement with Omega 3

Men's Health Recommendations: 
Women's Health Recommendations: Repeat your mammogram yearly and your pap smear every 1 - 2 years.
Overview Notes: Ensure good sun protection even in winter and continue to follow up with the dermatologist as you have been.

Overview Notes: Ensure good sun protection even in winter and continue to follow up with the dermatologist as you have been.
Comment Key: LabTestNote
Comment Value: Overall good blood results. Marginally raised cholesterol and suboptimal vitamin D level
Special Investigation Notes: Nil

Overview Notes: Cholesterol: try to manage with lifestyle alone. Healthy diet, continue exercising, decrease your weekend alcohol consumption&manage stress. Supplement with Omega 3

Clinical Recommendations: 
Men's Health Recommendations: 
Women's Health Recommendations: Repeat your mammogram yearly and your pap smear every 1 - 2 years.
Overview Notes: Ensure good sun protection even in winter and continue to follow up with the dermatologist as you have been.

Women's Health Recommendations: -Menopausal changes can be difficult to navigate. Please speak to your doctor to find ways to help you through this period.
Overview Notes: Vit D: supplement with vit D and recheck in 4/12, aim for 50-80 ng/ml. VitD is important for your bones;mood and cognitive health. Has anti-inflammatory, anti-cancer properties.
Comment Key: VitalsRecommendation
Comment Value: None
Special Investigation Notes: Nil

Overview Notes: Ensure good sun protection even in winter and continue to follow up with the dermatologist as you have been.
